git clone https://github.com/egg1245/se-toolkit-hackathon
cd se-toolkit-hackathon
docker-compose up
# Visit http://localhost:8000
```

### Testing

Run automated tests:
```bash
bash integration_test.sh
```

Manual testing: Follow TESTING.md guide

### Performance

- Async operations throughout (FastAPI, SQLAlchemy)
- Database query optimization with proper indexing
- Frontend lazy loading of translations
- localStorage for instant theme/language switching
- 30s timeout on LLM API calls

### Security

- Input validation on all API endpoints
- SQL injection prevention (parameterized queries)
- CORS disabled (single-origin deployment)
- No sensitive data in localStorage (only preferences)
- Protected default appliances from modification

### Backwards Compatibility

❌ **NOT compatible with v1.0 clients**
- API contract changed (appliance → appliance_ids)
- Response schema changed (appliance → appliances array)
- Frontend must be updated to use new API

